## Re-Add Procedure

1. Copy extension folder from `themes/` to `%APPDATA%\Cursor\extensions\`.
2. Add `package.json` with `contributes.themes`.
3. Add `themes/<name>-color-theme.json` with `colors` and `tokenColors`.
4. Add `.vsixmanifest` in extension root.
5. Register extension in `%APPDATA%\Cursor\extensions\extensions.json`.
6. Reload Cursor window and pick theme in `File -> Preferences -> Themes -> Color Themes`.
